  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Several scenarios can call for a return/refund in RepairQ. Follow the links below for a detailed walkthrough of handling each refund scenario. </p><p>Note: In most cases, you are required to open a VCT before you can perform a return transaction.</p><h3 id=\"VirtualCashTerminal(VCT)RefundResources-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933639827\" rel=\"nofollow\">Assign a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT) to Accept Payments</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2348187679\" rel=\"nofollow\">Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT) Ticket Payment Settings</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933279378/Control%20-%20f79824.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"VirtualCashTerminal(VCT)RefundResources-Refunds:ReturnItemsBacktoInventoryandIssueaRefundonanOpenTicket\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933541546/Refunds+Return+Items+Back+to+Inventory+and+Issue+a+Refund+on+an+Open+Ticket\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933541546\" data-linked-resource-version=\"13\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Refunds: Return Items Back to Inventory and Issue a Refund on an Open Ticket</a></h2><ul><li><p>A customer has changed their mind about their purchase before the ticket was closed, but after payment was collected.</p></li></ul><h2 id=\"VirtualCashTerminal(VCT)RefundResources-Refunds:IssueaPartialRefundforaPriceOverrideorDiscountonanOpenTicket\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933672585/Refunds+Issue+a+Partial+Refund+for+a+Price+Override+or+Discount+on+an+Open+Ticket\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933672585\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Refunds: Issue a Partial Refund for a Price Override or Discount on an Open Ticket</a></h2><ul><li><p>A price change (price override or discount) needs to be performed after collecting payment on the original price of the item <strong>before</strong> the ticket is closed.</p></li></ul><h2 id=\"VirtualCashTerminal(VCT)RefundResources-Refunds:IssueaRefundforaPriceAdjustmentonaClosedTicket\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933377724/Refunds+Issue+a+Refund+for+a+Price+Adjustment+on+a+Closed+Ticket\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933377724\" data-linked-resource-version=\"11\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Refunds: Issue a Refund for a Price Adjustment on a Closed Ticket</a></h2><ul><li><p>A price change (price override or discount) needs to be performed after collecting payment on the original price of the item <strong>after</strong> the ticket is closed.</p></li></ul><h2 id=\"VirtualCashTerminal(VCT)RefundResources-Refunds:ExchangeanItemandRefundtheDifference(PartialRefund)\"><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933475999/Refunds+Exchange+an+Item+and+Refund+the+Difference+Partial+Refund\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933475999\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Refunds: Exchange an Item and Refund the Difference (Partial Refund)</a></h2><ul><li><p>Item is exchanged after payment was collected and after the ticket was closed.</p></li></ul><p /><p /><p>START 1.18.X</p>",
